\delta H=\sum_{r=1}^n \dot q_r \delta p_r-\dot p_r\delta q_r
\frac{dq_r}{dt}=\frac{\partial H}{\partial p_r},\quad \frac{dp_r}{dt}=-\frac{\partial H}{\partial q_r},\quad (r=1.\dots,n)
